originalText.text: It’s an ok experience. It’s a little strange transferring between such beautiful new creation’s mixed in with such old, dusty, artifacts and creations created by past creators. I look forward to creating some new creations so that our Potential Future-Past grandchildren have a chance at the same Equal Opportunity’s afforded to all creations afforded the opportunity to create the creation they imagine themselves to create. I look forward to cleaning up and restoring the old creations because they were created first. They went to live as long as possible.
